      <br>
      <p>Even if the sound bar blocks the TV’s remote control signal, the IR Flasher on the back of the sound bar repeats the signal from the remote control so TV operation is unaffected.</p>
      <p>Similar to the IR Repeater, a sound bar with an IR Extender will repeat the control signal to your TV through a supplied IR extender cable ensuring peace of mind when placing the sound bar.</p>
      <p><img src="images/ir.jpg" width="100%" ></p>
