        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-4100</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-5100</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>The sound bar can ’learn‘ the TV’s remote control signals so you can use the TV remote control to turn the sound bar on and off and also adjust its volume.</p>
      <p>When the sound bar is connected via HDMI (compatible models), CEC is used to perform this function.</p>
      <p><img src="images/system-learning.jpg"></p>
    </div>
