      </table>
      <br>
      <p>Yamaha’s IntelliBeam sound bar calibration system takes the difficulty out of setting-up your new sound bar.</p>
      <p>This patented feature ensures optimal surround sound reproduction. Using the supplied microphone, IntelliBeam analyses the acoustic properties of the room and automatically sets the best beam angles while optimising the level and frequency response of each sound beam.</p>
      <p>Similar to YPAO technology, IntelliBeam streamlines the initial setup and provides professionally calibrated audio in the home.</p>
      <p><img src="images/intellibeam.jpg"></p>
